Website: https://www.ihlau.net

Additional FortyTwo BBS contributors are recorded in the Git history.


Project heritage
----------------

FortyTwo BBS is a modified and independently maintained continuation of
MBSE BBS. MBSE BBS was originally created by Michiel Broek and was later
maintained by the MBSE BBS Development Team.

The following individuals were listed in the inherited source tree as
MBSE BBS developers or contributors.

We, the developers of FortyTwo BBS, appreciate the work that has gone into
MBSE BBS and will continue to develop FortyTwo BBS in the spirit of open
source.

